    <item>
      <title>美联储利率信号提振工业金属，铜价恢复上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/copper-resumes-rally-as-fed-rate-signals-boost-industrial-metals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铜价本周恢复涨势，触及11个月高点，美联储释放出将满足降息预期的信号，提振了风险偏好并削弱了美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/copper-resumes-rally-as-fed-rate-signals-boost-industrial-metals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 02:19:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国建筑商光辉集团美元债券意外违约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/china-builder-radiance-defaults-on-dollar-bond-amid-sales-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国开发商金辉控股集团有限公司(Radiance Holdings Group Co.)周三未能按期付款，导致其3亿美元债券违约，这对过去几天押注及时还款的投资者来说是一个打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/china-builder-radiance-defaults-on-dollar-bond-amid-sales-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 01:38:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
