    <item>
      <title>交易员从美联储获得“金发姑娘”前景并推高市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/traders-get-goldilocks-outlook-from-fed-and-drive-up-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们已经准备好迎接杰罗姆·鲍威尔(Jerome Powell)推翻他们对降息的乐观态度——当他没有这样做时，买入信号在华尔街闪现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/traders-get-goldilocks-outlook-from-fed-and-drive-up-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 23:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市因美联储利率信号而在科技股带动下上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街创下新高后，亚洲股市上涨，因美联储暗示尽管通胀上升，但今年仍将进行三次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 22:50:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡将于下周开始债券重组谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/sri-lanka-to-start-restructuring-talks-with-investors-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，全球投资者和斯里兰卡官员预计下周将开始谈判，旨在重组价值 120 亿美元的全球违约债券。该国的美元债券上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-20/sri-lanka-to-start-restructuring-talks-with-investors-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Mar 2024 20:03:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
